subject: Horse Racing
Breeders' Cup (Horse Races)
lead_paragraph: Game On Dude, who lost in the Breeders’ Cup Classic last year, was one of 180 horses, including eight defending or former champions, entered in the 15 Breeders’ Cup races Nov. 2-3 at Santa Anita.
